title: Huush - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Huush performing live at the Conservatoire de Rennes 
Auditorium in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2023. Recorded December 7, 2023. 

Songs:
Disorder
Falling in Love
Follow the Beat

Hélie Maujard - Guitar, Vocals
Owen Rousselle - Bass, Vocals
Dan Voisin - Drums, Vocals

Audio Engineer: Matt Ogaz
Guest Audio Engineer: Fabrice Bayard
Audio Mixer: Dan Eshkovitch
Mastering: Dan Eshkovitch
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro, Scott Holpainen
Editor: Carlos Cruz
